		<h3 class="why">Why Nimbus?</h3>
		<p>- By focusing on only one goal at a time, you minimize switch costs that result from multitasking and maximize your cognitive resources for this particular goal.</p>
		<p>- Through reflection questions, you attribute meaning and insights to the actions you take. This helps to enhance your self-efficacy.</p>
		<p>- With self-affirmations, you maintain a positive outlook and validate your efforts.</p>
